TrackPlotter

Stand-alone ROOT application to plot tracks.
This application runs on the ValidationNtuple written by the
BasicValidationNtupleTool (from Tracking/TrkValidation/TrkValTools)
resp. TrackValidationNtupleWriter (from Tracking/TrkValidation/TrkValAlgs).

compile this tool by:
make trackplotter

to run:
./trackplotter
or 
./trackplotter TrkValidation.root

This tool needs a correctly set up ROOT installation.
If you get the message "cannot run in batch mode", please make sure
you have a valid X11 connection.
